* This is a RESTFUL API application done with Python and Django.
* This web application allow weathermen to query data from the database as and when they need it. 
* Midterm project for Advanced Web Development module.
* Frontend design is still under development.

Video Demo of this web application is available at: https://youtu.be/L98DBkxv0hg 

# Django admin superuser
# username: student
# password : simplepass123 

# ############# How to run the application:###############
# Navigate to this file: cd weather_app
# Create virtual environment: python3 -m venv myvenv
# Navigate to virtual environment: cd ../myvenv/bin
# Activate virtual environment:  source activate
# Install a new application : pip3 install schedule
# Install django : pip3 install django ‘or’ python3 -m pip install django
# Install REST Framework : pip3 install djangorestframework
# Navigate to this file: cd weather_project
# Populate database with csv file: python3 ./scripts/loadRecord.py
# python3 manage.py makemigrations
# python3 manage.py migrate
# Run server: python3 manage.py runserver
# open http://127.0.0.1:8000/







